<paragraph blockId="9.[144,1104,1546,1642]" box="[144,242,1546,1570]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1740">
<heading box="[144,242,1546,1570]" fontSize="10" level="3" pageId="9" pageNumber="1740" reason="5">
<emphasis box="[144,242,1546,1570]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="1740">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[144,1104,1546,1642]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1740">
Omnivorous and invasive species, minor plant pest, it may prey on other gastropods (
<bibRefCitation author="Barker GM" box="[151,291,1618,1642]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1740" refId="ref8757" refString="Barker GM. 2004. Natural enemies of terrestrial Molluscs. Wallingford (UK): CABI Publishing." type="book" year="2004">Barker 2004</bibRefCitation>
). UA, I.
</paragraph>
